plyTime":"2019-07-24T09:18:13.000Z","msg":"咁如果發出反對 會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T09:34:51.000Z","msg":"咁就以後遊行就唔申請, 唔申請佢點樣反對? 我係佢就唔會咁蠢"},{"pid":"4e5713864ae58a48cdf23f305738ca13c9c709be","tid":1360032,"uid":3822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T09:38:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e3e3ff9e62d25f0d0711c51a5c94dfae98cbabe3","tid":1360032,"uid":36845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T09:44:08.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有不反對通知書，咁就係合法遊行<br />\n警犬無反應，咁都係合法遊行<br />\n但係警犬都有權出反對通知書<br />\n有無咁難明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"f50d537fe56c7f9a29ea9a89a19ee5ee0cc35658","tid":1360032,"uid":122676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T09:52:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f941831a8514dbaf49f28c6fe5441578c9c3af26","tid":1360032,"uid":262557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T09:54:17.000Z","msg":"依個要推"}]}